1
00:03:22,950 --> 00:03:26,680
冰河世纪

2
00:03:52,580 --> 00:03:56,280
为什么不管这叫“大寒”或者“冷冻时代”
Why not call itthe Big Chill or the Nippy era?

3
00:03:56,350 --> 00:03:59,380
我是说我们怎么知道这是“冰川时代”？
I'm just saying,how do we know it's an ice age?

4
00:03:59,490 --> 00:04:02,110
因为四周全是冰！
Because of all the ice.

5
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:07,080
就连说话也冷冰冰的
Well, things just got a little chillier.

6
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:10,760
救命
Help. Help.

7
00:04:10,860 --> 00:04:14,160
来吧，孩子，我们走，大伙儿都在走呢！
Come on, kids, let's go. The traffic's moving.

8
00:04:14,530 --> 00:04:16,560
可是，可是，可是，爸爸
But, but, but, Dad.

9
00:04:16,700 --> 00:04:19,470
别说“可是”还轮不到你绝种呢
No buts. You can play extinction later.

10
00:04:19,740 --> 00:04:23,160
噢，OK，走吧，伙计们
OK. Come on, guys.

11
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:25,540
我说……艾迪在哪儿？
So, where's Eddie?

12
00:04:25,650 --> 00:04:29,430
啊，他说他马上就要出现一个“进化上的突破”了
He said he was on the vergeof an evolutionary breakthrough.

13
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:31,540
是吗？
Really?

14
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:34,750
噢，我飞了！
I'm flying.

15
00:04:36,090 --> 00:04:38,250
好一个突破
Some breakthrough.

16
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:41,920
小心！你走错方向了！
- Look out.- You're going the wrong way.

17
00:04:42,930 --> 00:04:44,990
你这毛象疯子！
Crazy mammoth.

18
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:56,540
嘿！你就帮个忙吧！别挡着道妨碍交通！
Do the world a favor.Move your issues off the road.

19
00:04:56,910 --> 00:05:01,070
如果我也是短鼻子我就不会那么抢眼了，老弟！
If my trunk was that small,I wouldn't draw attention to myself, pal.

20
00:05:01,250 --> 00:05:04,880
别臭我了我们……都挪了一整天了
Give me a break.We've been waddling all day.

21
00:05:06,690 --> 00:05:09,450
那就接着走吧，随大流吧
Go ahead. Follow the crowd.

22
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:11,750
你们走了就清静了
It'll be quieter when you're gone.

23
00:05:12,890 --> 00:05:15,880
走吧，他要冻死就随他去
Come on. If he wants tofreeze to death, let him.

24
00:05:25,970 --> 00:05:28,070
嘿，嘿，我醒了，醒了
I'm up. I'm up.

25
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:35,300
大家都快起来吧！呃？扎克？马歇尔？
Rise and shine, everybody.Huh? Zak? Marshall?

26
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:38,680
伯蒂？“真菌”叔叔？
Bertie? Uncle Fungus?

27
00:05:39,290 --> 00:05:45,510
大家都去哪儿了？来吧，伙计们，我们该迁…该迁…迁徙了
Where is everybody? Come on, guys,we're gonna miss the migration.

28
00:05:48,130 --> 00:05:52,480
扔下我就走了他们每年…都这么干！
They left without me.They do this every year.

29
00:05:54,500 --> 00:05:57,490
为什么？谁都不爱我了吗？
Why? Doesn't anyone love me?

30
00:05:57,870 --> 00:06:02,190
难道谁都不关心我这可怜的树懒希德了吗？
Isn't there anyone who cares about Sid the Sloth?

31
00:06:04,880 --> 00:06:07,040
好吧，那我就自己走
All right, I'll just go by myself.

32
00:06:09,750 --> 00:06:11,340
噢，恶心！
Sick.

33
00:06:11,450 --> 00:06:14,110
嘿，巨无霸！别随地大小便！
Wide body, curb it next time.

34
00:06:14,220 --> 00:06:16,710
噢，天，噢，唉唷！噢！
Oh, jeez. Yuck.

35
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:22,620
真不敢相信，新鲜绿叶菜弗兰克，你在哪儿找到的？
I can't believe it. Fresh wild greens.Frank, where did you ever...?

36
00:06:22,700 --> 00:06:25,860
好了，快吃吧是蒲公英？
- Go ahead. Dig in.- A dandelion.

37
00:06:25,930 --> 00:06:29,530
还以为都被冻死了就剩下这一棵
- I thought the frost wiped 'em all out.- All but one.

38
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:34,770
唷,唷,这实在让我太我要咬他的…啊
It makes me so... I wanna... Yuck.

39
00:06:34,870 --> 00:06:39,700
我呸！今天我算是倒霉透了我的意思你应该懂吧？
This has definitely not been my day.You know what I'm saying, buddy?

40
00:06:39,780 --> 00:06:43,510
简直一团糟，你们犀牛的脑袋实在是小，你们知道吗？
What a mess. You rhinos have tiny brains. Did you know that?

41
00:06:43,580 --> 00:06:49,340
这是事实，我没有恶意也许我的话你们根本不懂
It's just a fact. No offense. You probably didn't even know what I'm talking about.

42
00:06:49,460 --> 00:06:50,720
呵呵呵呵，噢，美味呀！
Yummo.

43
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:53,920
是蒲公英呀！一定是最后一棵了
A dandelion. Must bethe last one of the season.

44
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:59,360
卡尔？冷静，弗兰克
- Carl.- Easy, Frank.

45
00:06:59,470 --> 00:07:01,490
他糟蹋了我们的色拉
He ruined our salad.

46
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:05,670
呃，呃，噢，噢，是我错了
My mistake. That was my mistake. Let me...

47
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:10,030
伙计们，我错了，我赔我赔呃，这是什么？
No, no, seriously, let me take care of this. What is this?

48
00:07:10,110 --> 00:07:13,810
是松果啊！噢，老天，我最爱吃了！
Pine cones. Oh, my goodness.They're my favorite.

49
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:20,210
唔，味道好极了嗷，这真…呃，真好吃
Delicious. That's good eating.

50
00:07:20,450 --> 00:07:23,810
你们可不能让我独享了你们也吃点
But don't let me hog them all up.Here, you have some.

51
00:07:23,890 --> 00:07:26,690
味道不错吧？祝你们胃口好
Tasty, isn't it? "BON APPITITE(法语)."

52
00:07:28,060 --> 00:07:30,220
上吗？
Now?

53
00:07:30,660 --> 00:07:32,760
上
Now?

54
00:07:41,670 --> 00:07:45,700
假装我不在我是想全速把他撞倒
- Just pretend that I'm not here.- I wanted to hit him at full speed.

55
00:07:45,780 --> 00:07:51,070
别急，我们“玩玩”他.别让他们刺穿我，拜托了，我想活命
- That's OK. We'll have some fun with him.- Don't let them impale me. I wanna live.

56
00:07:51,150 --> 00:07:54,510
你走开！行了，你就别撒泼了
- Get off me.- Come on, you're making a scene.

57
00:07:54,590 --> 00:07:57,390
我们只要把那毛小子戳爆然后就走
We'll just take our furry pinata and go.

58
00:07:57,490 --> 00:08:00,480
嘿，小子，逃得了今天也逃不过明天
If it's not them today,it's someone else tomorrow.

59
00:08:00,530 --> 00:08:02,890
反正我今天不想死，OK？
Well, I'd rather it not be today. OK?

60
00:08:03,030 --> 00:08:06,390
听着，我们戳断你的脖子你不会痛苦的，怎么样？
We'll break your neck so you don't feel a thing.

61
00:08:06,470 --> 00:08:09,590
等一下，你们犀牛应该是食草动物吧？
Wait a minute. I thought rhinos were vegetarians.

62
00:08:09,700 --> 00:08:11,830
真精辟！闭嘴！
- An excellent point.- Shut up.

63
00:08:11,900 --> 00:08:15,530
谁说我们把他杀了之后要吃他？
Who says we're gonna eat him after we kill him?

64
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:18,530
我不喜欢以杀为乐的动物
I don't like animals that kill for pleasure.

65
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:22,070
谁爱听…就跟谁说吧恰好我就爱听
- Save it for a mammal that cares.- I'm a mammal that cares.

66
00:08:22,310 --> 00:08:27,480
好吧,如果你们俩有谁过得了前面这个坑，树懒就归你们
OK, if either of you make it across that sinkhole in front of ya, you get the sloth.

67
00:08:27,550 --> 00:08:31,440
没错，孬种往前跨一步就死定了！
That's right, you losers.You take one step and you're dead.

68
00:08:35,660 --> 00:08:39,260
你在吓唬他们？对，这“坑”不会沉
- You were bluffing, huh?- Yeah. Yeah, that was a bluff.

69
00:08:40,430 --> 00:08:42,160
收拾他！
Get him.

70
00:09:18,140 --> 00:09:20,260
是蒲公英？
A dandelion?

71
00:09:23,210 --> 00:09:25,270
哇！我们胜利了！
We did it.

72
00:09:33,650 --> 00:09:37,440
你的眼睛真美！快滚下我的脸！
- You have beautiful eyes.- Get off my face.

73
00:09:38,660 --> 00:09:42,750
噢，你和我，我俩配合默契不如结伴一起去南方吧
Whoa, we make a great team.What do you say we head south together?

74
00:09:42,860 --> 00:09:45,350
好啊，耶！嘿，跳到我背上来一路放轻松
Great. Jump on my backand relax the whole way.

75
00:09:45,430 --> 00:09:47,460
哇噢，当真？
- Wow, really?- No.

76
00:09:47,730 --> 00:09:52,060
等等，你不去南方？季节的变换，迁徙的本能
Wait, aren't you going south?The change of seasons, migration instincts.

77
00:09:52,140 --> 00:09:54,900
这些挺耳熟吧？不，再见了
- Any of this a-ringing a bell?- I guess not. Bye.

78
00:09:54,970 --> 00:09:57,900
好吧，多谢帮忙我自己走吧
OK, then. Thanks for the help.I can take it from here.

79
00:09:58,980 --> 00:10:02,680
嘿，你象只大号的鼬鼠有种等我们下来
You overgrown weasel.Wait till we get down there.

80
00:10:03,450 --> 00:10:07,240
何必一窝蜂地去南方又热又挤的，没意思
That south thing is way overrated.The heat, the crowds - who needs it?

81
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:11,880
还是这样好，你和我两个单身汉在荒野中闲逛
Isn't this great? You and me,two bachelors knocking about in the wild.

82
00:10:11,990 --> 00:10:15,780
不，你是想要保镖生怕自己被活吞了
No, you just want a bodyguard so you don't become somebody's side dish.

83
00:10:15,930 --> 00:10:18,260
你这家伙还真够精明的
You're a very shrewd mammal.

84
00:10:18,330 --> 00:10:21,290
那你带路吧先生，你叫…叫啥来着？
OK, lead the way, Mr Big...Didn't get the name.

85
00:10:21,370 --> 00:10:23,390
曼福雷德曼福雷德？难听
- Manfred.- Manfred? Yuck.

86
00:10:23,500 --> 00:10:28,740
不如叫“曼尼-忧郁的毛象”“曼尼-深沉的愁思者…曼尼…”
How about Manny the Moody Mammoth?Or Manny the Melancholy... Manny the...

87
00:10:31,210 --> 00:10:33,300
别再跟着我
Stop following me.

88
00:10:34,980 --> 00:10:40,810
好吧，好吧，你有心事听着，你就当我不在，我会闭嘴
OK, so you've got issues. You won'teven know I'm here. I'll just zip the lip.

89
00:11:24,860 --> 00:11:28,790
噢，你快瞧啊那可爱的…小宝宝，迭戈
Look at the cute little baby, Diego.

90
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:36,600
把他拿来当早餐一定很美妙没有他怎么能算早餐？
- lsn't it nice he'll be joining us for breakfast?- It wouldn't be breakfast without him.

91
00:11:36,710 --> 00:11:42,500
尤其因为他爸爸杀了我们一半的同胞，穿上我们的毛皮取暖
Especially since his daddy wiped out halfour pack and wears our skin to keep warm.

92
00:11:42,580 --> 00:11:45,710
以牙还牙，你看怎么样？
An eye for an eye, don't you think?

93
00:11:45,820 --> 00:11:49,380
让那人知道跟剑齿虎斗是什么下场
Let's show him what happens when he messes with sabers.

94
00:11:49,490 --> 00:11:52,690
通知大伙儿，我们黎明进攻
Alert the troops. We attack at dawn.

95
00:11:53,730 --> 00:11:58,320
迭戈，把那孩子带来，要活的
And, Diego, bring me that baby alive.

96
00:11:58,400 --> 00:12:03,650
如果要好好享受报仇那最好是活吞
If I'm gonna enjoy my revenge,I want it to be fresh.

97
00:12:25,090 --> 00:12:27,250
噢，累死我了
Phew. I'm wiped out.

98
00:12:27,590 --> 00:12:31,260
你用这点过夜？嘿，你块头大，你有很多木头
- That's your shelter?- You're a big guy. You got a lotta wood.

99
00:12:31,330 --> 00:12:34,130
我是小不点儿所以只要半根
- I'm a little guy.- You got half a stick.

100
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:40,590
可…有我的小木棍和我高度进化的脑子…我能生出…火！
But with my little stick and my highly evolved brain, I shall create fire.

101
00:12:41,010 --> 00:12:42,800
了不起
Fascinating.

102
00:12:43,140 --> 00:12:47,200
看看智慧是不是能战胜蛮力你瞧着吧
We'll see if brains triumph over brawn tonight. Now, won't we?

103
00:12:53,220 --> 00:12:55,480
嘿，我看见火花了
Think I saw a spark.

104
00:12:59,390 --> 00:13:02,950
呃，我能不能进来跟你一块挤一挤，曼尼老伙计？
Any chance I could squeeze in there with you, Manny, ol' pal?

105
00:13:03,060 --> 00:13:05,550
呃，你还是去烦别的家伙吧
Isn't there someone else you can annoy?

106
00:13:05,660 --> 00:13:09,230
朋友、亲戚或者毒蛇什么的
Friends? Family? Poisonous reptiles?

107
00:13:09,570 --> 00:13:14,300
我全家丢下了我他们不管我…自己迁徙了
My family abandoned me.They just kinda migrated without me.

108
00:13:14,370 --> 00:13:17,040
他们去年还要过分
You should see what they did last year.

109
00:13:17,110 --> 00:13:19,870
他们很早醒来然后绑住我的手脚
They woke up early andtied my hands and feet

110
00:13:19,950 --> 00:13:22,740
用田鼠塞住我的嘴并且把洞门堵上
and they gagged me with a field mouse,

111
00:13:22,850 --> 00:13:26,480
他们走水路这样我就闻不出它们的气味
covered their tracks, went through water so I'd lose their scent,

112
00:13:26,550 --> 00:13:29,390
反…反正…我也不需要他们
and... who needs 'em, anyway?

113
00:13:33,930 --> 00:13:36,290
你怎么样？有家庭吗？
So what about you? You have family?

114
00:13:40,500 --> 00:13:43,660
好吧，看来你累了我们天亮再谈
OK, you're tired. I see.We'll talk more in the morning.

115
00:13:46,210 --> 00:13:49,730
曼福雷德！你挪过去点好吗？
Manfred? Manfred?Could you scooch over a drop?

116
00:13:50,910 --> 00:13:53,940
噢，得了哪会这么快就睡着的！曼尼！
Come on. Nobody falls asleep that fast.

117
00:13:53,980 --> 00:13:56,070
曼尼
Manny

118
00:16:46,920 --> 00:16:49,080
迭戈来了，我们撤
There's Diego. Fall back.

119
00:16:55,660 --> 00:16:58,520
小孩在哪儿？在瀑布那儿追丢了
- Where's the baby?- I lost it over the falls.

120
00:16:58,730 --> 00:17:01,220
你追丢了？
You lost it?

121
00:17:04,070 --> 00:17:06,660
我要那小孩，迭戈我能找到
- I want that baby, Diego.- I'll get it.

122
00:17:06,740 --> 00:17:10,440
但愿如此不然的话被活吞的就是你
You'd better, unless you want to serve as a replacement.

123
00:17:10,610 --> 00:17:13,910
我们去“半峰”山去那儿会合
We'll go up to Half Peak. Meet us there.

124
00:17:15,280 --> 00:17:17,340
最好把他活着带来
It had better be alive.

125
00:17:18,650 --> 00:17:21,140
能完成这任务吗？迭戈？
Can we trust you with that, Diego?

126
00:17:21,250 --> 00:17:23,740
我们走！
Let's go.

127
00:17:46,550 --> 00:17:50,540
她看见我肩上的那根毛就说如果你找别的女伴风流
She picked a hair off my shoulder and says,"lf you have an extra mating dance,

128
00:17:50,650 --> 00:17:53,240
至少找一个毛的颜色相同的
at least pick a female with the same color pelt."

129
00:17:53,390 --> 00:17:56,780
我想“完了”我要成她的盘中餐了
I thought "Whoa. She's gonna go praying mantis on me."

130
00:17:56,920 --> 00:18:00,590
如果你有了配偶就该对她忠诚，你很幸运了
If you find a mate, you should be loyal.In your case, grateful.

131
00:18:00,660 --> 00:18:03,990
你给我走开一辈子守着一个太蠢了
- Now get away from me.- I think mating for life is stupid.

132
00:18:04,060 --> 00:18:06,290
那也太亏了我这“能干”的希德
There's plenty of Sid to go around.

133
00:18:07,800 --> 00:18:09,890
曼尼？
Manny?

134
00:18:10,500 --> 00:18:12,590
曼尼？
Manny?

135
00:19:05,420 --> 00:19:07,920
快瞧啊，他没事
Look at that. He's OK.

136
00:19:20,240 --> 00:19:22,900
他妈妈不见了
She's gone.

137
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:34,880
你是不是忘了什么？
- Manny, are you forgetting something?- No.

138
00:19:36,250 --> 00:19:40,280
可…可你刚救了他可上次救的那个我还没甩掉呢
- But you just saved him.- I'm trying to get rid of the last thing I saved.

139
00:19:40,360 --> 00:19:42,880
你不能把他留在这儿
But you can't leave him here.

140
00:19:46,900 --> 00:19:50,460
瞧，有烟他的那群人在山上
Look, there's smoke.That's his herd right up the hill.

141
00:19:50,700 --> 00:19:54,660
我们把他送回去我跟你说白了吧，根本没有“我们”
- We should return him.- Let's get this straight. There is no "we."

142
00:19:54,740 --> 00:20:00,370
从来就没有“我们”，其实没有我，这会我连“你”都没了
There never was a "we." In fact,without me, there wouldn't even be a "you."

143
00:20:01,310 --> 00:20:08,170
只是去山上你给我仔细听好，我就是不去！
- Just up the hill.- Listen very carefully: I'm not going.

144
00:20:08,450 --> 00:20:13,350
行啊，做你的混球，我会照顾他的噢，好，太好了
- Fine, be a jerk. I'll take care of him.- Yeah, that's good.

145
00:20:13,460 --> 00:20:16,880
你连自己都照顾不了我倒要瞧瞧
You can't even take care of yourself.This, I gotta see.

146
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:21,250
我送你回去我们不需要那坏蛋毛象，对吗？
I'll return you. We don't need that meany-weeny mammoth, do we?

147
00:20:21,330 --> 00:20:23,490
不需要他
No, we don't.

148
00:20:52,930 --> 00:20:56,320
你真给大自然丢脸这你知道吗？
You're an embarrassment to nature.Do you know that?

149
00:20:56,940 --> 00:21:00,170
小菜一碟，我行，我行
Piece of cake. I'm fine, I'm fine.

150
00:21:00,240 --> 00:21:02,260
我会送命的
I'm gonna die.

151
00:21:15,650 --> 00:21:17,210
曼尼
