他长得不怎么样可要找个顾家的太难了
He's not much to look at,but it's so hard to find a family guy.

308
00:36:16,520 --> 00:36:20,010
可不是嘛那些细腻的都被吃光了
Tell me about it.All the sensitive ones get eaten.

309
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:24,160
不，曼尼，我求你了我需要他
No, no, no. Manny, please,I'm begging you. I need him.

310
00:36:24,260 --> 00:36:27,860
怎么，小帅哥还用泡妞？得了，你别寒碜我了
- A good-looking guy like you?- You say that, but you don't mean it.

311
00:36:28,170 --> 00:36:32,450
不，我当真，瞧瞧你那两个小姐都被你迷晕了
No, seriously. Look at you.Those ladies, they don't stand a chance.

312
00:36:32,540 --> 00:36:36,030
你这幽默感还真刻毒我不想搅你的好事
- You have a cruel sense of humor.- Don't let me cramp your style.

313
00:36:36,110 --> 00:36:39,130
谢谢，曼尼，真够朋友，够哥们别带孩子去
- Thanks, Manny. You're a pal.- Without Pinky.

314
00:36:39,280 --> 00:36:41,570
我需要他
Manny, I need him.

315
00:36:45,180 --> 00:36:48,240
小姐们，说到哪儿了？
So, ladies, where were we?

316
00:36:48,520 --> 00:36:51,250
卡尔镇静，弗兰克
- Carl.- Easy, Frank.

317
00:36:53,920 --> 00:36:58,250
看见漂亮妞，他就象头猎豹至于那老虎
Pretty tail walks by, suddenly he moves like a cheetah. And that tiger...

318
00:36:58,330 --> 00:37:02,100
那“跟踪大师”连树懒都找不到
Yeah, Mr Great Tracker.Can't even find a sloth.

319
00:37:02,200 --> 00:37:06,060
我成什么了？奶妈？你在看什么，小捣蛋？
What am l? The wet nurse?What are you looking at, bone bag?

320
00:37:08,310 --> 00:37:12,040
瞧瞧你，你会长成一个大猛兽
Look at you. You're gonna grow into a great predator.

321
00:37:12,480 --> 00:37:16,830
哼，我看不会，你有什么只有一撮毛
I don't think so. What have you got?You got a little patch of fur.

322
00:37:16,910 --> 00:37:19,470
没有尖牙，没有利爪
No fangs, no claws.

323
00:37:19,550 --> 00:37:22,910
你的皮和肉是那么…软绵绵
You're folds of skin wrapped in mush.

324
00:37:23,320 --> 00:37:26,020
你有什么可怕的？
What's so threatening about you?

325
00:37:31,160 --> 00:37:34,150
嘿，这不是“动物园”里摸小动物
Does this look likea petting zoo to you? Huh?

326
00:37:37,070 --> 00:37:40,660
好吧，耍小聪明？该罚你坐一会儿了
OK. All right, wise guy.You just earned a time-out.

327
00:37:43,510 --> 00:37:46,640
噢，你觉得好玩？那这个呢？
You think that's funny? How about this?

328
00:37:48,750 --> 00:37:51,540
猫头鹰会吃了你
You'll be a little snack for the owls.

329
00:37:53,250 --> 00:37:56,450
你这小鬼还挺勇敢
You're a brave little squirt, I'll give you that.

330
00:38:02,390 --> 00:38:04,090
谢天谢地！谢天谢地！
Thank goodness. Thank goodness.No.

331
00:38:05,600 --> 00:38:07,090
有…老虎！
A tiger.

332
00:38:07,200 --> 00:38:09,690
救命！救命！
Help. Help.

333
00:38:09,830 --> 00:38:12,030
孩子在哪儿？噢，他没事，曼尼带着
- Where's the baby?- Manfred has him.

334
00:38:12,100 --> 00:38:16,300
快“咬”住我快，他咬住我了！
Just put me in your mouth.Come on. Hurry up. He got me.

335
00:38:17,210 --> 00:38:18,300
噢，救命
Help.

336
00:38:18,410 --> 00:38:21,000
你别来烦我他往这边跑了
- Get away from me.- It went this way.

337
00:38:21,810 --> 00:38:24,080
这儿！
Over here.

338
00:38:31,820 --> 00:38:34,310
噢，卡尔！老虎抢先得手
Carl. The tiger beat us to him.

339
00:38:35,760 --> 00:38:38,350
检查一下
Wait a minute.

340
00:38:43,330 --> 00:38:45,760
没错，他的确死了
He's dead all right.

341
00:38:45,870 --> 00:38:48,030
食肉动物就是开心
Carnivores have all the fun.

342
00:38:50,670 --> 00:38:55,340
我也不想那么伤他们的心我是迫不得已
Gosh, I hate breaking their hearts like that. But you know how it is.

343
00:38:56,150 --> 00:38:58,840
好吧，谢谢，可以把我放下了
All right, thanks. You can put me down now.

344
00:38:59,420 --> 00:39:01,480
曼尼,曼尼
Manny. Manny.

345
00:39:01,920 --> 00:39:05,840
我们不是急着赶路吗？迭戈，把他吐出来
Guys, I thought we were in a hurry.And Diego, spit that out.

346
00:39:05,920 --> 00:39:09,020
别弄脏了嘴
You don't know where it's been.

347
00:39:09,090 --> 00:39:12,860
妈呀，刚才有一会儿我还以为你真要吃了我
Boy. For a second there,I thought you were gonna eat me.

348
00:39:12,930 --> 00:39:16,060
我不吃烂杂碎我还以为
- I don't eat junk food.- Thought you were gonna...

349
00:39:16,130 --> 00:39:18,620
我真以为你…你想吗？
I thought you were gonna... Were you?

350
00:39:21,410 --> 00:39:26,230
等等我，慢点，慢点你们能等我一下吗？
Come on, wait up. Wait up. Come on,come on. Can you wait a second, please?

351
00:39:26,310 --> 00:39:28,400
嘿，伙计们
Fellas.

352
00:39:29,750 --> 00:39:31,840
谢谢等我
Thanks for waiting.

353
00:39:31,920 --> 00:39:34,650
3、2、1
Three, two, one...

354
00:39:37,550 --> 00:39:39,650
确实挺“忠诚”
Sure is faithful.

355
00:39:54,510 --> 00:39:56,700
再闹，我就要火了噢，是他引起的
- Don't make me reach back.- He started it.

356
00:39:56,770 --> 00:40:00,040
我不管谁引起的，再闹就罚！
I don't care who started it. I'll finish it.

357
00:40:32,880 --> 00:40:35,730
现代建筑，撑不了多久的
Modern architecture. It'll never last.

358
00:40:50,160 --> 00:40:52,250
嗨哟,曼尼
Hiya, Manny.

359
00:40:54,130 --> 00:40:56,390
嗨，迭戈．
Hi, Diego.

360
00:41:03,240 --> 00:41:05,300
嘿，希德．
Hey, Sid.

361
00:41:05,710 --> 00:41:09,480
你迷路了，对吗？没有，我很清楚我们在哪儿
- You're lost.- No. I know exactly where we are.

362
00:41:09,550 --> 00:41:11,910
让他指指方向
Ask him directions.

363
00:41:11,980 --> 00:41:14,680
我不要他指方向算了，我来问他
- I don't need directions.- Fine, I'll ask him.

364
00:41:14,790 --> 00:41:17,880
嘿，伙计你看见有人类经过吗？
Buddy. You see any humans go by here?

365
00:41:21,500 --> 00:41:24,380
呜,我喜欢猜字,OK
I love this game. I love this game. OK, OK.

366
00:41:24,500 --> 00:41:28,960
三个字,第一个字呃…“跺”,不,“踩”
Three words. First word.Stomp. No, no. Stamp, stamp.

367
00:41:29,070 --> 00:41:31,200
我猜猜,呃…“群”!
Let me try. Pack.

368
00:41:31,370 --> 00:41:35,540
猜得好,曼尼,“一群”长牙…和爪子
Good one, Manny.Pack of long teeth and claws.

369
00:41:37,110 --> 00:41:39,140
一群狼?一群…
Pack of wolves? Pack of...

370
00:41:39,210 --> 00:41:41,940
呃,一群熊!一群跳蚤?
Pack of bears? Pack of fleas?

371
00:41:42,020 --> 00:41:44,110
一群胡须?一群…鼻子?
Pack of whiskers? Pack of noses?

372
00:41:44,520 --> 00:41:46,780
呃…厚皮动物?一群谎言!
- Pachyderm?- Pack of lies.

373
00:41:46,890 --> 00:41:49,810
一群麻烦!一群打手!呃，一群鸟!
Pack of troubles. Pack a wallop.Pack of birds.

374
00:41:50,090 --> 00:41:52,150
一群飞鱼
Pack of flying fish.

375
00:42:40,860 --> 00:42:43,350
嘿!好消息!我找到一条近路!
Great news. I found a shortcut.

376
00:42:46,260 --> 00:42:49,860
什么近路?就是走着要比走长路快
- What do you mean, shortcut?- I mean faster than the long way around.

377
00:42:50,800 --> 00:42:52,600
噢!我知道什么叫“近路”!
I know what a shortcut is.

378
00:42:52,670 --> 00:42:57,920
我们穿过去就能比人类先到“冰川道”不然就会错过他们
Either we beat the humans to Glacier Passor we take the long way and miss 'em.

379
00:42:58,210 --> 00:43:01,730
穿过那儿?你把我当什么了?
Through there? What do you take me for?

380
00:43:01,810 --> 00:43:05,270
明天这个时候你…就可以自由了
This time tomorrow,you could be a free mammoth.

381
00:43:05,680 --> 00:43:08,380
或继续做保姆玩“躲躲猫”我是不会腻的
Or a nanny. I never get tired of peekaboo.

382
00:43:08,550 --> 00:43:11,380
伙计们,瞧这个
Guys. Guys. Check this out.

383
00:43:13,750 --> 00:43:16,250
老虎找到一条近路
Sid, the tiger found a shortcut.

384
00:43:18,390 --> 00:43:20,450
不,谢谢,我想活命
No, thanks. I choose life.

385
00:43:20,590 --> 00:43:23,190
那我建议你最好还是走近路
Then I suggest you take the shortcut.

386
00:43:23,300 --> 00:43:27,150
你在威胁我吗?走,树懒!
- Are you threatening me?- Move, sloth!

387
00:43:32,170 --> 00:43:34,660
好样的,老虎
Way to go, tiger.

388
00:43:34,710 --> 00:43:37,230
快!快进去!
Quick. Get inside.

389
00:43:59,930 --> 00:44:02,560
好吧,那就走近路吧
OK, I vote shortcut.

390
00:44:17,150 --> 00:44:20,810
好了,伙计们,都跟紧些这儿很容易走丢
Guys, stick together.It's easy to get lost in here.

391
00:44:36,440 --> 00:44:38,500
呃…伙计们?
Guys?

392
00:44:55,860 --> 00:44:57,880
啊!小鱼儿
A fish.

393
00:45:40,200 --> 00:45:44,370
你跟上,行不行?看住一个宝宝已经够难的了
Will you keep up, please?Hard enough to keep track of one baby.

394
00:46:29,580 --> 00:46:31,640
我…抓住你了
I gotcha.

395
00:46:48,300 --> 00:46:50,830
船长,前方有冰山!
Captain, iceberg ahead.

396
00:46:57,240 --> 00:46:59,300
哦，不
Oh, no.

397
00:47:50,630 --> 00:47:53,490
谁想玩第二回合?
Yeah. Who's up for round two?

398
00:47:57,400 --> 00:47:59,460
叫…叫…叫孩子小心点
Tell the kid to be more careful.

399
00:48:40,750 --> 00:48:43,600
瞧,瞧,老虎,瞧啊
Look, look. Tigers.

400
00:48:45,650 --> 00:48:50,410
不,没事的,没事的瞧,老虎和羚羊在做游戏
No, it's OK, it's OK. Look, the tigers are just playing tag with the antelope.

401
00:48:52,460 --> 00:48:56,990
捉到摸一下,用牙摸来吧,希德,我们也来玩
- With their teeth.- Come on, Sid, let's play tag.

402
00:48:57,060 --> 00:48:59,160
你捉我
You're it.

403
00:49:00,300 --> 00:49:03,500
行啊…好吧,好吧哪儿画着树懒?
Sure. OK, OK, OK, where are the sloths?

404
00:49:03,570 --> 00:49:06,430
这上面怎么没画树懒?你们注意到吗?
You never see any sloths.Have you ever noticed?

405
00:49:06,540 --> 00:49:10,430
瞧,曼尼,一头毛象噢,我可真兴奋
- Look, Manny, a mammoth.- Somebody pinch me.

406
00:49:10,540 --> 00:49:13,400
嘿,嘿,这头胖的看上去可真象你
Hey, hey, this fat one looks just like you.

407
00:49:14,310 --> 00:49:16,610
噢,他有家庭
And he's got a family.

408
00:49:16,720 --> 00:49:20,110
他很幸福瞧,他在陪孩子玩
And he's happy.Look, he's playing with his kid.

409
00:49:20,190 --> 00:49:24,420
瞧,曼尼,这就是你的问题毛象应该象他们那样
See? That's your problem.That's what mammoths are supposed to do.

410
00:49:24,420 --> 00:49:27,150
找头母象…生一头毛象宝宝
- Find a she-mmoth, have baby mammoths...

411
00:49:27,150 --> 00:49:28,010
希德
- Sid.

412
00:49:28,010 --> 00:49:29,460
干嘛?闭嘴
- What?- Shut up.

413
00:49:29,520 --> 00:49:31,160
可…噢
But...

414
00:52:58,270 --> 00:53:00,470
噢,快瞧啊
Would you look at that.

415
00:53:00,570 --> 00:53:03,600
老虎没带错路这是“半峰山”
The tiger actually did it. There's Half Peak.

416
00:53:03,740 --> 00:53:06,410
下一站,冰川道
Next stop, Glacier Pass.

417
00:53:06,810 --> 00:53:10,600
我真不该怀疑你你听见吗,小家伙?
- How could I ever have doubted you?- Did you hear that, little fella?

418
00:53:10,680 --> 00:53:12,780
你快到家了
You're almost home.

419
00:53:17,490 --> 00:53:20,020
我的脚在冒汗你身体每出现一个反应
- My feet are sweating.- Do we need a news flash

420
00:53:20,090 --> 00:53:23,480
我们都得发布新闻?他要我们注意他
- every time your body does something?- lgnore him.

421
00:53:23,600 --> 00:53:26,790
是真的我的脚真的很烫!噢,噢
Seriously. My feet are really hot.

422
00:53:32,510 --> 00:53:34,840
是你的肚子在叫吧?
Tell me that was your stomach.

423
00:53:34,910 --> 00:53:37,170
嘘,我肯定是那是雷声
I'm sure it was just thunder.

424
00:53:37,440 --> 00:53:40,370
声音…来自…地下?
From underground?

425
00:54:00,600 --> 00:54:02,760
快,跟我一起跑
Come on, keep up with me.

426
00:54:02,840 --> 00:54:05,630
可你原地不动!
I would if you were moving.

427
00:54:08,010 --> 00:54:11,210
哇,但愿我也能跳成全你了!
- I wish I could jump like that.- Wish granted.

428
00:54:15,580 --> 00:54:19,970
快!跑快点!难道你没看到熔岩流吗?
- Come on, move faster.- Have you noticed the river of lava?

429
00:54:39,210 --> 00:54:41,270
抱紧他!
Hold Pinky.

430
00:55:12,770 --> 00:55:14,900
曼尼
Manny.

431
00:55:26,350 --> 00:55:31,020
曼尼,你没事吧?求你说点什么,什么都行
Manny, Manny, Manny, you OK?Come on, come on, say something. Anything.

432
00:55:33,430 --> 00:55:35,490
什么?什么?我听不清
What? What? I can't hear you.

433
00:55:35,660 --> 00:55:37,890
你站在我的鼻子上了
You're standing on my trunk.

434
00:55:39,970 --> 00:55:43,390
啊,你没事!你没事你为什么那么干?
- You're OK. You're OK.- Why did you do that?

435
00:55:43,470 --> 00:55:46,230
你冒死…救了我的命
You could have died, trying to save me.

436
00:55:46,640 --> 00:55:49,230
大家是一个集体
That's what you do in a herd.

437
00:55:49,310 --> 00:55:51,470
得互相照顾
You look out for each other.

438
00:55:51,650 --> 00:55:53,980
噢!谢谢
Well, thanks.

439
00:55:56,120 --> 00:56:00,640
不知你们怎么想,可我觉得我们这“集体”是最怪的
I don't know about you guys,but we are the weirdest herd I've ever seen.

440
00:56:19,010 --> 00:56:22,070
我的爪子都快等不及要撕烂那毛象了!
I can't wait to getmy claws in that mammoth.

441
00:56:22,180 --> 00:56:25,960
谁都不能碰那毛象除非我先得到…孩子!
No one touches the mammoth until I get that baby.

442
00:56:29,350 --> 00:56:32,010
首先,我要把那毛象撕开扯烂
First, I'll slice its hindquarters into sections.

443
00:56:32,090 --> 00:56:36,280
把白色肉放一堆,深色…嘿,别再说了!我饿坏了!
- I'll put the white meat in one pile and...- Knock it off. I'm starving.

444
00:56:36,390 --> 00:56:40,090
肩膀的肉…可能比较老但绝对多汁
Next, the shoulders. Occasionally tough, but extremely juicy.

445
00:56:40,190 --> 00:56:43,390
警告过你了,别再说了!省点力气吧!
- I told you to knock it off.- Save your energy.

446
00:56:43,500 --> 00:56:46,490
要杀毛象谈何容易
Mammoths don't go down easy.

447
00:56:46,770 --> 00:56:49,060
只有一个办法
There's only one way to do it.

448
00:56:49,200 --> 00:56:51,760
首先,得把他逼上死角
First, you have to force it into a corner.

449
00:56:52,610 --> 00:56:56,430
切断他的退路等你们三个把他困住
Cut off its retreat.And when you three have it trapped,

450
00:56:56,680 --> 00:56:58,800
我就咬断他的喉咙
I'll go for the throat.

451
00:57:08,720 --> 00:57:11,520
伙计们,别让孩子吹着风!
Guys, we gotta get this kid outta the wind.

452
00:57:15,800 --> 00:57:18,060
还有多远?三英里
- How much further?- Three miles.

453
00:57:18,160 --> 00:57:21,550
我累坏了,我们早上能到
I'm beat. We'll get there in the morning.

454
00:57:24,670 --> 00:57:28,330
你在干嘛?我让树懒…名垂千古
- What are you doing?- I'm putting sloths on the map.

455
00:57:31,210 --> 00:57:34,410
那得画得现实点画他在睡觉
Why don't you make it realistic and draw him lying down?

456
00:57:34,480 --> 00:57:36,570
画得“圆”一些
And make him rounder.

457
00:57:39,090 --> 00:57:42,870
好极了哈!我真笑不出来
- Perfect.- I forgot how to laugh.

458
00:57:50,300 --> 00:57:52,390
我是个天才
I'm a genius.

459
00:57:56,070 --> 00:58:00,960
从现在起,你们得称呼我“希德-火焰之王”
From now on you'll have torefer to me as Sid, Lord of the Flame.

460
00:58:01,110 --> 00:58:04,600
嘿,火焰之王,你尾巴着火了
Lord of the Flame, your tail's on fire.

461
00:58:12,620 --> 00:58:16,610
噢,谢谢,从现在起我就管你叫…“迭戈”
Thank you. From now on,I'm gonna call you Diego.

462
00:58:16,720 --> 00:58:19,020
“摸我你是死定之王”
Lord of "Touch Me and You're Dead".

463
00:58:19,130 --> 00:58:22,250
我是说着玩的你这没头脑的
I'm just kidding, you little knucklehead.

464
00:58:22,800 --> 00:58:24,990
嘿,小俩口
Lovebirds.

465
00:58:25,130 --> 00:58:27,190
快瞧
Look at this.

466
00:58:31,140 --> 00:58:33,200
这简直……太神了
I don't believe it.

467
00:58:46,650 --> 00:58:51,650
过来,小家伙过来,你这小虫虫
Come here, you little biped.Come here, you little wormy-worm.

468
00:58:51,760 --> 00:58:53,950
到希德叔叔这儿来
Come to Uncle Sid.

469
00:58:54,060 --> 00:58:57,090
这边,这边
No, no... This way. This way.

470
00:58:58,200 --> 00:59:00,830
不,去他那儿
No, no, no. No, go to him.

471
00:59:01,970 --> 00:59:04,030
去他那儿
Go to him.

472
00:59:06,440 --> 00:59:07,740
好吧
OK.

473
00:59:09,110 --> 00:59:12,810
干得好,接着…练习吧
Good job. Keep practicing.

474
00:59:15,750 --> 00:59:18,950
快瞧啊,我们的小家伙在长大
Look at that. Our little guy is growing up.

475
00:59:21,220 --> 00:59:24,250
好了,过来该睡了,肉团儿
All right, come on. Sleep time, lumpy.

476
00:59:29,930 --> 00:59:31,990
他对孩子就是亲
Look at that big pushover.

477
00:59:33,600 --> 00:59:37,920
要知道,迭戈我还没有能冒死救我的朋友呢
You know, Diego, I've never hada friend who would risk his life for me.

478
00:59:38,470 --> 00:59:42,700
是啊,曼尼他…他真好
Yeah, Manny's... he's a good guy.

479
00:59:43,140 --> 00:59:45,200
是啊,的确
Yeah, he is.

480
00:59:45,880 --> 00:59:48,370
好了,晚安
Well, good night.

481
01:00:20,450 --> 01:00:26,010
让我给你弄干净,你这么又脏又臭的回去,你老爸会怎么说?
Let's get you all cleaned up. What's your daddy gonna say if you go back all stinky?

482
01:00:26,850 --> 01:00:30,910
我来擦干净,嗯,好多了这儿还有点儿
Let me just clean that up.That looks good. A little bit here.

483
01:00:31,020 --> 01:00:34,850
擦干净真漂亮,小家伙他长得越来越象我了
- You clean up nice, little fella.- I think he's starting to look like me.

484
01:00:34,930 --> 01:00:37,060
嘿,迭戈,你说呢?
Diego, what do you think?

485
01:00:38,730 --> 01:00:41,120
也许不该送回去为什么?
- Maybe we shouldn't do this.- Why not?

486
01:00:41,230 --> 01:00:45,020
因为他长大后会成为猎人你说他会猎杀谁?
If we save him, he'll be a hunter.And who do you think he'll hunt?

487
01:00:45,240 --> 01:00:47,630
也许救了他他就不会成猎人
Maybe because we save him,he won't hunt us.

488
01:00:47,840 --> 01:00:52,300
是啊,也许他会长出毛和长脖然叫你“妈妈”
Yeah, and maybe he'll grow fur anda long skinny neck and call you Mama.

489
01:00:52,880 --> 01:00:58,240
你怎么回事?没什么,我们走,冻死我了
- What's your problem?- Nothing. Let's go. I'm freezing my tail off.

490
01:01:17,570 --> 01:01:19,660
嘿,迭戈,你被冻住了吗?
Diego. You frozen back there?

491
01:01:23,980 --> 01:01:25,970
低下身子!什么?
- Get down.- What?

492
01:01:26,050 --> 01:01:28,310
嘘,低下身跟我走嘿,怎么回事?
- Get down and follow me.- What's going on?

493
01:01:28,410 --> 01:01:33,440
在半峰山脚下有个埋伏…等着你们
At the bottom of Half Peak,there's an ambush waiting for you.

494
01:01:33,520 --> 01:01:35,850
什么?你说什么“埋伏”?
- What?- What do you mean, "ambush"?

495
01:01:38,060 --> 01:01:40,220
你设了圈套!那是我的任务!
- You set us up.- It was my job.

496
01:01:40,290 --> 01:01:43,890
我得把孩子抢到手,可是你把我们带回家当晚餐
- I was to get the baby, but then...- You brought us home for dinner.

497
01:01:44,000 --> 01:01:46,800
行了!你被开除了!真对不起
- That's it. You're out of the herd.- I'm sorry.

498
01:01:46,870 --> 01:01:48,930
我宰了你…你再后悔吧
No, you're not. Not yet.

499
01:01:49,140 --> 01:01:52,830
听着,我能帮你们跟紧了,希德,我们能杀出去!
- Listen, I can help you.- Stay close, Sid. We can fight our way out.

500
01:01:53,010 --> 01:01:56,200
不行!他们太强大了你们得信任我
You can't. The pack's too strong.You have to trust me.

501
01:01:56,280 --> 01:01:59,540
信任你?我们干嘛要信任你?
Trust you? Why in the world would we trust you?

502
01:01:59,650 --> 01:02:01,640
因为你们只有靠我
Because I'm your only chance.

503
01:02:15,300 --> 01:02:17,350
哈罗,“小姐”们
Hello, ladies.

504
01:02:18,200 --> 01:02:23,690
嘿,瞧谁终于肯露脸了迭戈,我正为你担心呢
- Look who decided to show up.- Diego, I was beginning to worry about you.

505
01:02:23,800 --> 01:02:30,030
用不着担心,再过两分钟你将从…复仇中…得到满足
No need to worry. In about two minutesyou'll be satisfying your taste for revenge.

506
01:02:30,180 --> 01:02:31,870
这非常好
Very nice.

507
01:02:32,280 --> 01:02:35,370
我看见树懒了!孩子在他手里!
I see the sloth. And he's got the baby.

508
01:02:35,450 --> 01:02:40,810
没见到毛象就别暴露你们自己我们得出其不意
Don't give away your positions until yousee the mammoth. He's the one to surprise.

509
01:02:42,060 --> 01:02:44,550
你想重拳出击对吗,齐克?
You want to maul something, don't you?

510
01:02:44,620 --> 01:02:48,120
呵呵,我想出击那你还等什么?
- I wanna maul.- Then what are you waiting for?

511
01:02:51,230 --> 01:02:53,830
不,我说了等那毛象出现!
No, I said wait for the mammoth.

512
01:03:15,790 --> 01:03:18,950
“雪板挠背”你们吃白雪吧!嘿嘿
Backscratcher. Eat my powder!

513
01:03:34,570 --> 01:03:36,670
唷!喔!“环滑车”呃,啊!
Loop-de-loop.

514
01:03:37,680 --> 01:03:39,840
障碍滑雪,障碍滑雪，宝贝
Slalom! Slalom, baby!

515
01:04:05,470 --> 01:04:09,330
对不起,伙计们他被冻成小雪人了
Sorry, fellas. He got a little frostbite.

516
01:04:10,980 --> 01:04:13,040
呜!宰了他!
Get him.

517
01:04:16,050 --> 01:04:18,140
大惊喜!
Surprise!

518
01:04:23,060 --> 01:04:27,760
好吧,跟我来!我们去找希德,然后离开这儿
OK, follow me. We'll pick up Sidand get outta here while we can.

519
01:04:27,830 --> 01:04:31,790
来吧,迭戈我们把这毛象摆平
Come on, Diego,let's bring this mammoth down.

520
01:04:44,180 --> 01:04:46,480
他在这儿
There he is.

521
01:04:48,510 --> 01:04:51,010
没错,宝宝在哪儿啊?
That's right. Where's the baby?

522
01:04:54,890 --> 01:04:58,190
这就叫…适者…生存!
Survival of the fittest.

523
01:04:58,260 --> 01:05:00,210
这老虎不行
I don't think so. Yeah.

524
01:05:12,240 --> 01:05:16,770
你这是干嘛?不许…碰这…毛象
- What are you doing?- Leave the mammoth alone.

525
01:05:19,680 --> 01:05:22,740
好,我先把你摆平
Fine. I'll take you down first.

526
01:06:38,690 --> 01:06:40,780
我们赢了
We did it.

527
01:06:52,440 --> 01:06:56,270
我们曾经是多棒的集体
We were some team, huh?

528
01:06:56,980 --> 01:07:00,370
曾经是?胡说,我们还是一个集体
Were? Come on, we're still a team.

529
01:07:00,780 --> 01:07:03,340
我设下圈套,真对不起
I'm sorry I set you up.

530
01:07:03,850 --> 01:07:06,710
我就算恨你,也懒得记仇了
You know me -I'm too lazy to hold a grudge.

531
01:07:10,060 --> 01:07:12,150
嘿,别闹,小鬼
Knock it off, squirt.

532
01:07:13,060 --> 01:07:15,120
你得强壮些
You gotta be strong.

533
01:07:15,460 --> 01:07:18,790
你得照顾曼福雷德和希德
You have to take care of Manfred and Sid.

534
01:07:19,800 --> 01:07:21,820
尤其是希德
Especially Sid.

535
01:07:21,930 --> 01:07:25,790
行了,你能挺过来,你是老虎
Come on, you can lick this. You're a tiger.

536
01:07:25,870 --> 01:07:29,000
我能背你,你说怎么样?
Look, I'll carry you.Come on, what do you say?

537
01:07:29,140 --> 01:07:31,410
振作点,迭戈,振作!
Come on, Diego, come on.

538
01:07:31,480 --> 01:07:33,640
告诉他他会好的,曼尼
Tell him he's going to be OK, Manny.

539
01:07:35,210 --> 01:07:38,880
听着,你们别管我了
Listen, you have to leave me here.

540
01:07:38,990 --> 01:07:43,180
如果人类过了“冰川道”你们就找不到他们了
If those humans get through the pass,you'll never catch them.

541
01:07:43,820 --> 01:07:46,880
你不用救我的
You didn't have to do that.

542
01:07:46,990 --> 01:07:49,760
我们是一个集体
That's what you do in a herd.

543
01:11:05,490 --> 01:11:07,580
别忘了我们
Don't forget about us.

544
01:11:07,660 --> 01:11:09,750
好吗?
OK?

545
01:11:12,000 --> 01:11:14,690
我们不会忘了你
We won't forget about you.

546
01:11:54,410 --> 01:11:57,030
再见,再见
Goodbye.

547
01:11:57,180 --> 01:11:59,610
再见,再见
Goodbye.Goodbye.

548
01:11:59,710 --> 01:12:02,010
希德再见
- Sid...- Bye.

549
01:12:03,480 --> 01:12:05,470
再见
Bye.

550
01:12:08,190 --> 01:12:10,610
对,对,没错宝宝在哪儿
That's right. Where's the baby?

551
01:12:10,760 --> 01:12:13,250
走吧,希德,我们去南方
Come on, Sid, let's head south.

552
01:12:31,340 --> 01:12:33,330
再见
Bye.

553
01:12:34,410 --> 01:12:37,910
省口气吧,希德人类不会说话
Save your breath, Sid.You know humans can't talk.

554
01:12:38,420 --> 01:12:40,480
迭戈?你没事!
Diego? You're OK.

555
01:12:40,620 --> 01:12:42,710
我有九条命呢
- Nine lives, baby.- You're OK.

556
01:12:43,990 --> 01:12:46,080
你没事!
You're OK.

557
01:12:46,690 --> 01:12:48,790
我亲亲你!呀!呜
I could kiss ya.

558
01:12:50,430 --> 01:12:52,690
欢迎回来,搭挡,要我背吗?
Welcome back, partner. Wanna lift?

559
01:12:52,800 --> 01:12:55,790
不,谢谢我得保住仅存的那点尊严
No thanks. I gotta save whatever dignity I've got left.

560
01:12:55,940 --> 01:13:00,430
你跟我们混在一块了就别管什么尊严了吧,就背我吧
You're hanging out with us. Dignity'sgot nothing to do with it. I'll take that lift.

561
01:13:00,810 --> 01:13:02,970
好,爬上来吧托我一把,咿哈
- Yeah, climb aboard.- Pick me up, buddy.

562
01:13:03,040 --> 01:13:07,070
或者不说“驾”,随你喜欢
Mush. Or not mush. Either way.

563
01:13:10,780 --> 01:13:13,410
这将是我最棒的一次迁徙
This is gonna be the best migration ever.

564
01:13:13,490 --> 01:13:18,410
我带你们去我的宝地,我毛里的真菌干死后我会变成棕色
I'll show you my favorite watering holes.I turn brown when the fungus in my fur dries.

565
01:13:18,490 --> 01:13:22,280
这真有意思我说,这“冰川时代”可真没劲
- Attractive.- This whole lce age thing is getting old.

566
01:13:22,390 --> 01:13:25,750
知道我喜欢什么“全球变暖”
You know what I could go for?Global warming.

567
01:13:25,830 --> 01:13:28,890
做梦去吧我可是说真的
- Keep dreaming.- No, really...

568
01:13:34,710 --> 01:13:39,060
两万年以后
20,000 Years Later

569
01:15:23,900 --> 01:15:57,900
谢谢观看!

